	<entry>
		<title>On Life at Sea</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://nightland.website/index.php/about/william-hope-hodgson/199-on-life-at-sea"/>
		<published>2015-07-16T20:14:46+00:00</published>
		<updated>2015-07-16T20:14:46+00:00</updated>
		<id>https://nightland.website/index.php/about/william-hope-hodgson/199-on-life-at-sea</id>
		<author>
			<name>Kate Coady</name>
		</author>
		<summary type="html">&lt;div class=&quot;story-intro&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://nightland.website/index.php/about/william-hope-hodgson/199-on-life-at-sea&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;story-thumb&quot; src=&quot;https://nightland.website/images/thumbs/william-hope-hodgson-at-ships-wheel-thumb.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;William Hope Hodgson at a ship's wheel&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;story-teaser&quot;&gt;Hodgson was the great horror writer of the sea. Despite the focus of this site it is arguable that his best &lt;span class=&quot;emphasis&quot;&gt;short&lt;/span&gt; work is found in such stories as &quot;The Voice In The Night&quot;...&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
</summary>
		<content type="html">&lt;div class=&quot;story-intro&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://nightland.website/index.php/about/william-hope-hodgson/199-on-life-at-sea&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;story-thumb&quot; src=&quot;https://nightland.website/images/thumbs/william-hope-hodgson-at-ships-wheel-thumb.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;William Hope Hodgson at a ship's wheel&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;story-teaser&quot;&gt;Hodgson was the great horror writer of the sea. Despite the focus of this site it is arguable that his best &lt;span class=&quot;emphasis&quot;&gt;short&lt;/span&gt; work is found in such stories as &quot;The Voice In The Night&quot;...&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
